An online webinar was organised inviting CBO and CSO representatives working in Kampala and Wakiso. the purpose to explore their view on how to jointly influence access of child friendly services even during the COVID 19 crisis.

A radio talk show was then taken on where representatives from CBOs and key district leaders called upon all stakeholders to embark on child protection as they access equal distribution and access to friendly services.

Activities/ Engagements with UCATIP  were not conducted or spent on during the quarter as most organizations' operations were hit by the pandemic, thus rekindled after organizations re directed their work to the "new normal". therefore, engagements were planned for third quarter,;

